{"tid":1955926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下自己安全set 密碼嘅方法","createTime":"2020-04-02T21:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T01:30:30.000Z","uid":63452,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d045ba8d83f337a0b2d1352834d9a6f290f318","tid":1955926,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:58:03.000Z","msg":"我set 密碼嘅方法係分4 part:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[Base keyword]</span><span style=\"color: green;\">[用途]</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">[數字]</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">[符號]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Part 1: <span style=\"color: red;\">Base keyeord</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n首先set 一個英文字keyword 做我個密碼個base<br />\n個keyword 越奇怪越好，今次我用'FuckPoPo'，記住要有大細楷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Part 2: <span style=\"color: green;\">用途</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n第二part 都係英文字，會因應password 嘅用途而變<br />\ne.g. 連登就 'LIHKG'，gmail 就 'Google'<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Part 3&amp;4: <span style=\"color: blue;\">數字</span>同<span style=\"color: purple;\">符號</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n第三part 就可以自己任意揀啲數字同符號<br />\n我今次就用 '666' 同 '???' 做例子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁基本上我嘅所有密碼就用返一樣嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">[Base keyword]</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">[數字]</span>同<span style=\"color: purple;\">[符號]</span>，只係需要改<span style=\"color: green;\">[用途]</span>，<br />\n用我以上嘅例子:<br />\n我嘅連登password: <span style=\"color: red;\">FuckPoPo</span><span style=\"color: green;\">LIHKG</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">666</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">???</span><br />\n我嘅gmail password: <span style=\"color: red;\">FuckPoPo</span><span style=\"color: green;\">Google</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">666</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">???</span><br />\n當然大家可以改我唔同part 嘅次序，效果都係一樣<br />\n用呢個方法改密碼，你有100 個網站就可以有100 個唔同嘅password，就算你俾人知道左一個password 都無咁易爆到你其他網站嘅password<br />\n用呢個方法重有個好處就係如果你記性真係好差都可以抄底<span style=\"color: green;\">[用途]</span>個part，只要你記實其餘唔變嘅部分，唔好俾任何人知就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\">FuckPoPo</span><span style=\"color: green;\">LIHKG</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">666</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">???</span>放上網check 下有幾安全 ...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdyPWzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdyPWzm.jpg&h=f634ae32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我第一次見quintillion 呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle 返黎嘅US definition 係10^18，UK 係10^30，總之就要好撚多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個網直頭放棄左估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJRquV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJRquV5.jpg&h=6e273849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打有其他更好嘅改密碼方法，不妨分享下俾小弟同其他人學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果巴打重係用緊'password' 做password 嘅，就快啲加強自己啲密碼嘅強度，唔好俾壞人同Popo 有機可乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd485ec67a4863f1d2b4bc89c13c58f554b412b","tid":1955926,"uid":63311,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:58:56.000Z","msg":"pw generator gen 個128位再記住佢"},{"pid":"c342ce4ede50b4d5588cceadd7068531e4554278","tid":1955926,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8fd485ec67a4863f1d2b4bc89c13c58f554b412b","tid":1955926,"uid":63311,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:58:56.000Z","msg":"pw generator gen 個128位再記住佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:00:20.000Z","msg":"巴打you win，我都係出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=